message.raw:
Make subg_ign/GameLogicPlugin depend on subt_msgs generation

Build server failed with GameLogicPlugin not finding header generated
by subt_msgs package. This could happen as a race condition with
catkin_make if the GameLogicPlugin build does not explicitly depend on
completion of exported targets (e.g., header generation)

The following packages have unmet dependencies:
 ignition-blueprint : Depends: libignition-gazebo2-dev but it is not going to be installed
                      Depends: libignition-launch-dev but it is not going to be installed
